00:22:06.819 --> 00:22:08.099
Otherwise,

00:22:08.299 --> 00:22:10.980
I can have him perish anytime.

00:22:13.460 --> 00:22:14.339
Don't believe him.

00:22:15.099 --> 00:22:16.119
He just wants to use him,

00:22:16.119 --> 00:22:17.940
whether human or ghost, to control you.

00:22:18.688 --> 00:22:21.248
Immortal sects indeed manage
reincarnation across Three Realms.

00:22:21.859 --> 00:22:23.059
But it needn't be him.

00:22:30.059 --> 00:22:30.660
Yuan,

00:22:31.500 --> 00:22:32.259
