00:22:32.539 --> 00:22:33.140
Yuan?

00:22:34.180 --> 00:22:34.900
Where's the pain?

00:22:38.539 --> 00:22:39.339
Yuan?

00:22:40.099 --> 00:22:40.779
Well?

00:22:41.619 --> 00:22:42.779
Does it ache your heart?

00:22:43.500 --> 00:22:44.700
Is it agonizing?

00:22:45.220 --> 00:22:47.779
If you obey me from now on,

00:22:48.019 --> 00:22:49.940
I'll stop immediately.

00:22:50.220 --> 00:22:51.220
How about it?

00:23:02.940 --> 00:23:04.380
If I hear correctly,

00:23:05.400 --> 00:23:07.039
you're threatening me?

00:23:08.420 --> 00:23:10.619
Haven't measured your own worth?

00:23:14.900 --> 00:23:16.440
What gives you the right

00:23:17.180 --> 00:23:18.819
to dare bargain with me!

00:23:21.460 --> 00:23:23.500
Release Ye Chenyuan's restraints now!

00:23:24.019 --> 00:23:25.740
Or I'll kill you this instant!

00:23:37.180 --> 00:23:37.819
I

00:23:38.539 --> 00:23:39.420
agree.

00:23:46.339 --> 00:23:48.180
But during his revival,

00:23:48.819 --> 00:23:51.339
