I needed to stay busy

00:25:06.460 --> 00:25:07.220
and occupied

00:25:08.500 --> 00:25:09.099
so that

00:25:11.619 --> 00:25:13.220
I could briefly forget

00:25:14.579 --> 00:25:15.740
the pain of losing you.

